[base]
# Dataset Module
Vector generation and ground truth. dataset.rs: trait + types.
ground_truth.rs: brute-force KNN for recall. loader.rs: binary + HDF5 formats.
Recall = intersection(results, ground_truth) / K.

[debug]
Ground truth cached in .gt files — expensive to recompute.
If recall drops: check if dataset regenerated without updating ground truth.
HDF5: use h5dump to inspect dimensions.

[skill:debug:dataset-inspector]
# Dataset Inspector
Load header, sample vectors, verify ground truth dimensions, report stats.
